## Phase 7 ‚Äî Admin Endpoints & Production Hardening
**Goal**: Admin dashboard API, soft delete, soft freeze with reasons, and security hardening.

| Step | Domain | Task | Details |
|------|--------|------|---------|
| 7.1 | Controller | **Admin user management** | `GET /api/v1/admin/users` (paginated, searchable), `GET /api/v1/admin/users/{id}` (detail with wallet + KYC status), `GET /api/v1/admin/wallets` (all wallets with status filter) |
| 7.2 | Controller | **Admin wallet actions** | `PATCH /api/v1/admin/wallets/{id}/freeze` (with reason: SUSPICIOUS_ACTIVITY/ADMIN_ACTION/USER_REQUEST), `PATCH /api/v1/admin/wallets/{id}/unfreeze` |
| 7.3 | Controller | **Admin transaction search** | `GET /api/v1/admin/transactions` ‚Äî search by reference, wallet, user, date range, type, status |
| 7.4 | Controller | **Admin audit log view** | `GET /api/v1/admin/audit-logs` ‚Äî paginated, filterable by entityType, action, performedBy, date range |
| 7.5 | Controller | **Admin fee management** | Full CRUD on `FeeConfiguration`: `GET/POST/PUT/DELETE /api/v1/admin/fees` |
| 7.6 | Controller | **Admin KYC management** | `GET /api/v1/admin/kyc/pending` (pending documents), `POST /api/v1/admin/kyc/{docId}/approve`, `POST /api/v1/admin/kyc/{docId}/reject` (with reason), `POST /api/v1/admin/kyc/users/{userId}/downgrade` |
| 7.7 | Controller | **Admin virtual card management** | `GET /api/v1/admin/cards` (all cards), `PATCH /api/v1/admin/cards/{id}/freeze`, `PATCH /api/v1/admin/cards/{id}/close` |
| 7.8 | Controller | **Admin Flutterwave operations** | `GET /api/v1/admin/payments/transactions` (all payment txns), `GET /api/v1/admin/payments/webhook-log` (webhook history), `POST /api/v1/admin/payments/reprocess-webhook/{id}` (replay dead-letter) |
| 7.9 | Security | **Role-based access** | `@PreAuthorize("hasRole('ADMIN')")` on all admin endpoints |
| 7.10 | Enhancement | **Soft delete user** | `PATCH /api/v1/admin/users/{id}/deactivate` ‚Äî sets `deleted=true`, `deletedAt=now`, freezes wallet. `GET` filters out deleted by default |
| 7.11 | Enhancement | **Security headers audit** | Verify HSTS, CSP, XSS protection, content-type options. Add `Strict-Transport-Security` in production profile |
| 7.12 | Enhancement | **Input sanitization** | Strip/escape HTML from string inputs to prevent log injection and stored XSS (defense in depth) |
| 7.13 | Test | **Admin endpoint security tests** | Verify USER cannot access ADMIN endpoints (403) |

**Deliverable**: Complete admin API covering users, wallets, transactions, KYC, virtual cards, and Flutterwave operations. Soft delete, freeze reasons, role enforcement. Security hardening complete.

