## Phase 8 ‚Äî Testing & Quality Assurance
**Goal**: Comprehensive test coverage, not just happy paths.

| Step | Domain | Task | Details |
|------|--------|------|---------|
| 8.1 | Unit | **Service layer tests** | All services: `AuthService`, `KycService`, `KycLimitEnforcer`, `TransactionService`, `WalletService`, `FeeEngineService`, `AuditService`, `NotificationService`, `PaymentService`, `CardService` |
| 8.2 | Unit | **Security tests** | `JwtUtil`, `JwtAuthFilter`, `RateLimitingFilter`, `IdempotencyFilter` |
| 8.3 | Unit | **Fee engine edge cases** | Zero amount, max/min clamping, rounding scenarios, inactive config fallback, concurrent calculation |
| 8.4 | Unit | **KYC limit enforcement** | All tier levels, daily limit boundary, balance cap boundary, upgrade one-directional enforcement |
| 8.5 | Integration | **Full transaction flow** | H2-based: register ‚Üí KYC Tier 2 ‚Üí deposit ‚Üí transfer ‚Üí withdraw ‚Üí verify all balances, transaction records, audit logs |
| 8.6 | Integration | **Concurrent transfer test** | Spawn threads attempting simultaneous transfers from same wallet, verify no negative balance and correct final balance |
| 8.7 | Integration | **Idempotency end-to-end** | Send same `Idempotency-Key` twice, verify second call returns cached response, only one transaction recorded |
| 8.8 | Integration | **Rate limiting end-to-end** | Exceed rate limit, verify 429 with correct headers |
| 8.9 | Integration | **Refresh token rotation** | Full cycle: login ‚Üí refresh ‚Üí old token rejected after rotation ‚Üí reuse detection |
| 8.10 | Integration | **Scheduler idempotency** | Run pending cleanup twice, verify same FAILED count |
| 8.11 | Integration | **KYC document flow** | Upload ‚Üí PENDING ‚Üí admin approve ‚Üí tier upgrade ‚Üí limits enforced; upload ‚Üí PENDING ‚Üí admin reject ‚Üí re-upload ‚Üí approve |
| 8.12 | Integration | **Flutterwave webhook flow** | Create PENDING deposit ‚Üí receive webhook ‚Üí verify signature ‚Üí update SUCCESSFUL ‚Üí credit wallet; failed webhook ‚Üí FAILED ‚Üí no credit |
| 8.13 | Integration | **Virtual card lifecycle** | Fund card ‚Üí spend ‚Üí freeze ‚Üí unfreeze ‚Üí close ‚Üí return balance |
| 8.14 | Integration | **Admin authorization** | USER token gets 403 on admin endpoints, ADMIN token succeeds |

**Deliverable**: >85% code coverage on core business logic. All critical paths have integration tests. KYC, payment, and card flows fully tested.

