## Phase 11 ‚Äî Flutterwave Payment Integration ‚¨ÖÔ∏è EXPANDED
**Goal**: Live mobile money deposits, withdrawals, and card payments via Flutterwave with production-grade webhook handling, reconciliation, and error management.

| Step | Domain | Task | Details |
|------|--------|------|---------|
| 11.1 | Entity | **FlutterwaveTransaction entity** | `id (UUID)`, `userId`, `walletId`, `localTransactionId` (FK ‚Üí Transaction), `provider` (FLUTTERWAVE), `providerReference`, `flwRef` (webhook dedup), `type` (DEPOSIT/WITHDRAWAL/CARD_FUNDING), `amount`, `providerAmount`, `providerCurrency`, `exchangeRate`, `providerFee`, `status` (PENDING/SUCCESSFUL/FAILED/CANCELLED), `webhookReceivedAt`, `webhookPayload` (JSON), `reconciliationStatus` (UNMATCHED/MATCHED/DISCREPANCY), `createdAt`, `updatedAt` |
| 11.2 | Migration | **Flyway V13, V14** | `V13__create_flutterwave_transactions_table.sql`, `V14__create_webhook_dead_letter_table.sql` |
| 11.3 | Service | **PaymentService** | `initiateMobileMoneyDeposit(userId, walletId, amount, network, phoneNumber)` ‚Äî creates PENDING deposit, calls Flutterwave Payments API, returns payment reference; `initiateCardDeposit(userId, walletId, amount, redirectUrl)` ‚Äî creates PENDING deposit, calls Flutterwave Payments API (card), returns payment link; `initiateWithdrawal(userId, walletId, amount, pin, bankCode, accountNumber)` ‚Äî verify PIN + KYC limit, deduct wallet instantly, call Flutterwave Transfers API, create PENDING withdrawal record |
| 11.4 | Service | **WebhookService** | `handleFlutterwaveWebhook(payload, signature)` ‚Äî verify `Verif-Hash` header against secret, deduplicate via `flwRef` check, route to handler by event type (`charge.completed`, `charge.failed`, `transfer.completed`, `transfer.failed`), update transaction status, credit/debit wallet |
| 11.5 | Service | **PaymentReconciliationService** | `reconcilePendingTransactions()` ‚Äî `@Scheduled(fixedRate=900000)` ‚Äî query Flutterwave for status of pending transfers older than 15 min, update local records. `reconcileDailyLedger()` ‚Äî daily job comparing local Flutterwave transactions with Flutterwave's transaction list for discrepancy detection |
| 11.6 | Controller | **PaymentController** | `POST /api/v1/payments/deposit/mobile-money` (network, phone, amount), `POST /api/v1/payments/deposit/card` (amount, redirectUrl), `POST /api/v1/payments/withdraw` (amount, pin, bankCode, accountNumber), `GET /api/v1/payments/transactions` (user's payment history) |
| 11.7 | Controller | **WebhookController** | `POST /api/v1/webhooks/flutterwave` ‚Äî no auth (signature-verified), 30s timeout |
| 11.8 | Service | **FeeAbsorptionService** | `calculateUserCost(amount, transactionType)` ‚Äî if `FEE_ABSORPTION_MODE=USER_PAYS`, user's deposit = amount - Flutterwave fee; if `PLATFORM_PAYS`, platform absorbs fee, user gets full amount |
| 11.9 | Integration | **Flutterwave API client** | `FlutterwaveApiClient` ‚Äî HTTP client (RestClient/WebClient) wrapping Flutterwave REST API: `POST /payments`, `POST /transfers`, `GET /transfers/{id}`, `GET /transactions`, `POST /banks` (list banks). All calls include `Authorization: Bearer {secretKey}` |
| 11.10 | Integration | **Bank list & validation** | `GET /api/v1/payments/banks?country=ZM` ‚Äî fetch supported banks for withdrawal, cache for 24h |
| 11.11 | Error handling | **Webhook dead-letter** | If webhook handler throws exception after 3 retries ‚Üí save to `webhook_dead_letter` table with payload + error for admin review. Admin can replay via `POST /api/v1/admin/payments/reprocess-webhook/{id}` |
| 11.12 | Error handling | **Transfer failure reversal** | If withdrawal transfer FAILED (confirmed by webhook or reconciliation), automatically reverse the wallet debit: create reversal transaction, credit wallet, audit log entry, notify user |
| 11.13 | Config | **Flutterwave config** | `flutterwave.secret-key`, `flutterwave.public-key`, `flutterwave.webhook-secret`, `flutterwave.base-url` (sandbox vs production), `flutterwave.fee-absorption-mode` (USER_PAYS/PLATFORM_PAYS), `flutterwave.reconciliation-cron` in `application-prod.yml` |
| 11.14 | Security | **Webhook IP whitelist** | Flutterwave webhook endpoint should verify source IP (Flutterwave webhook IPs), configurable |
| 11.15 | Test | **PaymentService tests** | Mock Flutterwave API client, verify deposit/withdrawal initiation, error handling, timeout |
| 11.16 | Test | **WebhookService tests** | Valid signature ‚Üí processed; invalid signature ‚Üí 401; duplicate flwRef ‚Üí skipped; charge.completed ‚Üí wallet credited; transfer.failed ‚Üí reversal created |
| 11.17 | Test | **Reconciliation tests** | Pending older than 15 min ‚Üí polled; status mismatch ‚Üí DISCREPANCY logged |

**Deliverable**: Full Flutterwave integration ‚Äî mobile money deposits, card payments, bank withdrawals. Webhook-driven transaction completion with signature verification, deduplication, dead-letter queue, and automated reversal on failure.

