| Phase | Timeline | What |
|-------|----------|------|
| **10** ‚Äî Flutter Frontend | 3‚Äì4 weeks | Cross-platform mobile app: auth, KYC onboarding, dashboard, send money, card management, transaction history, push notifications |
| **11** ‚Äî Flutterwave Integration | 2‚Äì3 weeks | Mobile money deposits, card payments, bank withdrawals, webhook handling, reconciliation, dead-letter queue, transfer failure reversal |
