### Alternative Schedules

| Mode | Total Days | Per-Phase Pace | Trade-offs |
|------|-----------|----------------|------------|
| **Full (this plan)** | **25 days** | ~2 days per phase | Every day üü° balanced. Full KYC, Flutterwave (scaffolded), virtual cards, tests, Docker, CI/CD |
| **MVP (no KYC/cards)** | **16 days** | ~1.5 days per phase | Phase 0‚Äì5 only. No KYC (Tier 1 only, hardcoded limits), no virtual cards, no Flutterwave. Basic wallet P2P |
| **MVP + KYC** | **19 days** | ~1.5 days per phase | Phase 0‚Äì1.5 + 2‚Äì5. No virtual cards, no Flutterwave. KYC Tier 1‚Äì2 with document upload (manual approval only) |
| **Part-time (evenings)** | **8‚Äì9 weeks** | Same 25 days spread | ~3 days/week pace, good if employed or studying |
